# CrowdCare — always deploy

When you change **CrowdCare** app or API code in this repo (anything that affects production behavior or docs the team relies on):

1. Run **`npm run build`** from the repo root and fix failures.
2. Run **`npx vercel deploy --prod --yes`** from the repo root (same machine that has the linked Vercel project).
3. Confirm the deployment finished and **https://crowdcare.fund** is aliased to the new production deployment.

Do this **in the same session** as the edits unless deploy is impossible (no CLI, auth failure—then say so clearly). Do not end the task with “you can deploy” without running deploy when the environment allows it.
